articles.author: Helen Regan
articles.title: One dead, thousands evacuated as northeast Australia battles massive floods - CNN
articles.description: One person has died and thousands of others are under evacuation orders in Australia’s northeast after intense rain triggered dangerous flash floods that have inundated homes and businesses.
